	(text_box "Especificaciones: \n• TELEMETRY: 4ini Telemetry data port.\n• VCC：Battery Volt monitoring port with the battery voltage is to connect to the Battery Volt monitoring port\n on flight controller.\n• CRT：Amp monitoring port with the amperage of 11.75mv/A is to connect to the Amp monitoring port on\n flight controller. (conectaodo al ADC 1)\n• GND：Ground wire.\n• S1-4：Throttle Signal Input Ports. Port S1 is for ESC M1, S2 is for M2, S3 is for M3, and S4 is for M4.\n• POWER INPUT：power input soldering point , \"-\" for connecting the power wire - , \"+\" for connecting the\n power wire + ."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 19.05 66.04 0)
		(size 59.69 31.75)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
